OL,3,CPrincess Eugenie pregnant with third
OL,4,Cchild, Buckingham Palace announces
OL,6,FPrincess Eugenie and her husband Jack
OL,7,FBrooksbank are "very pleased" to be
OL,8,Fexpecting their third child to be born
OL,9,Fthis summer, Buckingham Palace has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe King is "delighted" with the news,
OL,13,Fwhile the couple's sons August, five,
OL,14,Fand Ernest, two, are "very excited" to
OL,15,Fwelcome a younger sister or brother to
OL,16,Fthe family, the palace said on Monday.
