OL,3,CPrincess Eugenie pregnant with third
OL,4,Cchild, Buckingham Palace announces
OL,6,FIn a photograph shared by Eugenie, 36,
OL,7,FErnest, wearing a Chelsea football
OL,8,Fkit, and August, wearing a long-
OL,9,Fsleeved grey t-shirt, can be seen
OL,10,Fholding a picture of a baby scan.
