OL,3,CPrincess Eugenie pregnant with third
OL,4,Cchild, Buckingham Palace announces
OL,6,FIn a statement, Buckingham Palace
OL,7,Fsaid: "Her Royal Highness Princess
OL,8,FEugenie and Mr Jack Brooksbank are
OL,9,Fvery pleased to announce that they are
OL,10,Fexpecting their third child together,
OL,11,Fdue this summer.
OL,13,F"August (aged five) and Ernest (aged
OL,14,Ftwo) are also very excited to have
OL,15,Fanother sibling join the family.
OL,17,F"His Majesty The King has been
OL,18,Finformed and is delighted with the
OL,19,Fnews."
