OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1777935793
OL,3,CPrincess Eugenie pregnant with third
OL,4,Cchild, Buckingham Palace announces
OL,6,FThe baby, who will not be an HRH, will
OL,7,Fbe born 15th in line to the throne,
OL,8,Fwith their great uncle the Duke of
OL,9,FEdinburgh, moving down to 16th place.
OL,11,FHe or she will also be the 15th great-
OL,12,Fgrandchild of the late Queen Elizabeth
OL,13,FII, and the third to be born since her
OL,14,Fdeath in 2022.
OL,16,FThe new arrival will be the fifth
OL,17,Fgrandchild of Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,18,FWindsor, following the birth of
OL,19,FPrincess Beatrice's daughter Athena
OL,20,FMapelli Mozzi in January last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
