OL,3,CPrincess Eugenie pregnant with third
OL,4,Cchild, Buckingham Palace announces
OL,6,FMr Brooksbank celebrated his 40th
OL,7,Fbirthday on Sunday, with the King's
OL,8,Fniece marking the occasion by sharing
OL,9,Fphotographs on her Instagram story of
OL,10,Fher husband relaxing on a beach with
OL,11,Fthe caption "happy 40th my love".
OL,13,FThe pair married in St George's
OL,14,FChapel, Windsor Castle, in October
OL,15,F2018, and welcomed their first child,
OL,16,FAugust, on February 9, 2021. His
OL,17,Fyounger brother Ernest was born on May
OL,18,F30, 2023.
